snippet.title: Breach - Official Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
www.playbreach.com

Modern Earth and Mythological Earth collide in Breach, a third person action RPG with fast-paced combat.  Create your own character and choose from dozens of classes.  Take your character on missions across the globe in Solo, Co-op, or Versus modes.  Loot new gear, earn new classes, and endlessly customize your character to find your own unique playstyle and look.  Every session is different with an all new kind of enemy, the Veil Demon.

----
Follow Breach on your favorite platforms:
- Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/PlayBreach
- Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/PlayBreach
- Discord: https://www.discord.gg/PlayBreach
